longBusinessSummary: DigiMax Global Inc., a technology company, provides advanced financial, predictive, and cryptocurrency solutions across various industries and verticals in Canada. Its products include Projected Personality Interpreter that empowers organizations with comparative insight for enhance hiring decisions, reducing employment attrition, and improving workplace culture; and Cryptohawk.Ai, a crypto price prediction indicator tools. The company was formerly known as DigiCrypts Blockchain Solutions Inc. and changed its name to DigiMax Global Inc. in May 2021. DigiMax Global Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Toronto, Canada.
